Good Grips Convertible Colander
<b>Good Grips Convertible Colander:</b>
*Perfect for draining pasta and for rinsing large batches of fruits, vegetables, herbs and more, even with a sink full of dishes
*Legs spring out to rest securely over sink and fold down for convenient storage
*Soft, comfortable, non-slip handles make shaking and pouring easier
*Non-slip surfaces protect sinks and counter tops during use
*Fits both single and double sinks either horizontally or vertically
*Measures 10 inches in length by 6 inches in width by 5 inches in height and holds 5 quarts

